	(135,'36','10','DISTRIBUTION','That portion of the system which is used to distribute high or low pressure air to using systems. Includes items such as ducts, valves, actuators, heat exchangers, controls, etc. Does not include the supply valves to the using systems.','2015-11-02 10:31:42','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
